Crown Crafts Inc said it expects toreport record sales and earnings for the June 28 first quarter.    The company said its prior record sales quarter was thesecond quarter of fiscal 1987 with sales of 15,097,000 dlrs.    Its prior record net earnings and primary earnings pershare of 877,000 dlrs, or 1.15 dlrs a share, were achieved inthe third quarter of fiscal 1987.    Crown also said its backlog stands at more than 17.0 mlndlrs, double the backlog a year ago. Reuter&#3;